snippet.title: The Serpent Rogue - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Try the demo on steam while it's up: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1453790/The_Serpent_Rogue/

The Serpent Rogue is an action-adventure game built around exploring a medieval fantasy world, mastering the art of alchemy, and taming wild creatures.
